Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不跟我們一起走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還有點事情要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處理完我馬上就會離開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，妳是說真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，我會馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的很喜歡妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳別忘記這點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果千繪是男生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定會迷上妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當是稱讚收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊，妳喜歡的是楯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，我們會等妳，妳一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切，明天就會全部結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就又可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:02:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不知道那位聰明的女性\N為什麼會做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，玖我博士非常重視妳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第25話 往命運的時刻\N我認為這是不容置疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我心中的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是因為人有重視的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為真的很重視
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會迷惘犯錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤乃同學也是因為對妳有著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛戀之情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為很重視妳\N所以才會那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣\N我根本不想談戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為有愛情\N人才能夠活得下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝妳一切順利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽，妳怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼那種臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又耍白痴了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說夏姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學校很快樂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道妳這麼喜歡唸書哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唸書…是有點那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我還是很喜歡那種\N跟同學在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快快樂樂嬉鬧的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說其實是一種痛苦哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是蹺課大王嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望今後能好好享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連過去的份一併努力玩回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果，那個破爛機器人\N還是沒找到就玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外…那個仿冒HiME也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡是些預料之外的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這樣子比較有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.43,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟過往不斷重複的玩意\N有著根本性的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然變了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這個容納用的軀體\N有所改變也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯準備好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳不要突然跑進來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，一不小心就習慣性…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實本來想弄得更豐盛點的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不禁就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是快煮拉麵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這拉麵可是我的拿手好菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最棒的拉麵唷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵果然很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也…不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣煮的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，舞衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道妳那淚水的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭唷，妳有我陪著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定會見到面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算非得一戰不可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留，我一定要把妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬，妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就可以將妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意是售後服務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳是大客戶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳合作很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概無法活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，能認識妳真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道妳該做什麼吧，命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎，去完成自古以來的契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照吾王的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻已到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台將開啟最後一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和我的妻子將會創造新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我通往英靈殿之門…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往地下神殿的路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們畢竟只是棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正該打倒的\N是策動這一切的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且先告訴妳這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想問妳，妳為何在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為妳力量來源的心愛之人\N明明已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是為了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我想要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此一個體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保有前次啟動時的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將之格式化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新設定主人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼重視艾莉莎的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始讀取
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是無法理解妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們分明就沒有\N如同我跟小姐之間的那種羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往神殿的入口在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來應該是那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學，等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是老樣子突然就出現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳所消滅的一番地本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有打倒的HiME們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再讓妳\N繼續做相同的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然不肯接受我的心意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清姬!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同歸於盡也要阻止妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兄長的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣，還是要請妳讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認艾莉莎．西爾斯的呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除一切拘束程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入麻痺射線機槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀套裝，緋紅模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈囉，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這種臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不會妨礙妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正和\N西爾斯的破銅爛鐵在玩耍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打壞那玩意\N可會有點不妙哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？妳要走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要是太老神在在\N可是會超過時限的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!我要去找命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜之王想要妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧我會引導妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的並不打算讓妳這麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是喜歡妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算妳會恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要得到妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要阻止妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賭上我自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.36,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心之子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經由對重視之人的心意\N而產生的異形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念之情的強度…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就這麼討厭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當HiME的心上人消失一名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封架的柱子就會\N吸收他的生命而升起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當12個HiME\N剩下最後一個人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑曜宮便會現出真正面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，多了一根呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說\N已經分出勝負了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不放手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我這個長久以來\N不願相信任何人的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個踏入我內心世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法抱持妳所期望的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是很高興妳喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳，靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杜蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝填銀彈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下靠妳了，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封架之宮要開啟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運在等待著妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡妳的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去以來我看過很多HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但妳是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了，舞衣公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳命還真硬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我不能讓妳過去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是水晶公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，來的好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的獲勝者是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，黑曜之王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲勝的HiME會被封架在水晶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為封架之宮的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化做引導媛星之力的閘門
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這次不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳將會在真正的意義上\N成為我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一同創造新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在多數神話中\N世界都是從一對男女開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這兩人結合後生出的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這個世界已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也很清楚吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是多麼沒道理\N多麼不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來跟我一起創造新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生出一個完美的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著各式各樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於那個人的珍貴心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳恨我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.46,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨是比愛情更強烈的執著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不恨你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得很悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼駕馭迦具土的人總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.31,0:20:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳想怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫出迦具土，並放棄這個世界\N而換取打倒我的機會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是楯祐一已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳弟弟也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳還叫得出迦具土嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經一無所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我以外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對祐一的心意填滿著我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認到艾莉莎．西爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動反物質裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀套裝，白金模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除所有保全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反物質裝置馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0…2…6
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破馬力界限
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.41,0:23:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.56,0:23:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀時光 （Shining Days）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的發生了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀時光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.40,0:00:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:24:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界總是背叛著我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.19,0:24:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一直這麼認為而活過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只充滿著對那些\N奪走我全部的人的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我活下來的唯一理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我察覺到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身邊有妳們在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有靜留 有舞衣 有命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.41,0:24:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有綻放笑容的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.29,0:24:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然還是像一把尖銳的小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.09,0:24:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，靜留對我抱持的好感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.96,0:24:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣和楯對彼此的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我發覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是無法孤獨活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一件很理所當然\N卻非常重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.74,0:24:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.35,0:25:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點不好意思\N但我還是要說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.05,0:25:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.15,0:25:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝陪在我身邊的所有人
